    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-03-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-03-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="395"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d395">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 815.00/1193.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-03-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 17, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. McCreery says at yesterday’s session the conference extended to him a vote of
                    thanks for his efficacious and opportune services to the body in its labors for
                    peace.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
